## 5. SEVERITY MODEL (from AUDIT.md)

```
// Rank every finding so Danny fixes the dangerous things first
BLOCKER  — security hole, secret leak, tenant data exposure, app-breaking
HIGH     — broken pattern, duplication that will bite, missing auth/escaping
MEDIUM   — file over cap, inconsistency, weak modularity
LOW      — naming, minor cleanup, missing comment
```

On the frontend, **secrets-in-client, auth handling, and tenant data leakage rank at
the top** — they go to BLOCKER regardless of how small the diff looks.

